ont-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; ">	</span>19</p><p class="toc-item" style="margin: 0px 0px 2pt 0.75cm; text-align: left; font-weight: bold;; font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; ">2.7 Karakteristik Fisik dan Fenotipe<span style="mso-tab-count:1; font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; ">	</span>21</p><p class="toc-item" style="margin: 0px 0px 2pt 0.75cm; text-align: left; font-weight: bold;; font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; ">2.8 Hukum Mendel dan Pewarisan<span style="mso-tab-count:1; font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; ">	</span>22</p><p class="toc-item" style="margin: 0px 0px 2pt 0.75cm; text-align: left; font-weight: bold;; font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; ">2.9 Pengertian Thalassemia<span style="mso-tab-count:1; font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; ">	</span>23</p><p class="toc-item" style="margin: 0px 0px 2pt 0.75cm; text-align: left; font-weight: bold;; font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; ">2.10 Pengertian Databse<span style="mso-tab-count:1; font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; ">	</span>24</p><p class="toc-item" style="margin: 0px 0px 2pt 0.75cm; text-align: left; font-weight: bold;; font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; ">2.11 MySQL<span style="mso-tab-count:1; font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; ">	</span>26</p><p class="toc-item" style="margin: 0px 0px 2pt 0.75cm; text-align: left; font-weight: bold;; font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; ">2.12 <i style="; font-family: Times New Roman; ">Unified Modeling Language</i> (UML)<span style="mso-tab-count:1; font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; ">	</span>27</p><p class="toc-item" style="margin: 0px 0px 2pt 0.75cm; text-align: left; font-weight: bold;; font-fami